<br>
In my book, if you can answer "Yes" to the following questions, your guild is a success.<br>
<br>
Does your guild make the time you spend on mindless exp camping more enjoyable?<br>
<br>
Do you want to log on and spend time with your guildmates?<br>
<br>
Are you achieving your goals as a player with your guild?<br>
<br>
Are you helping your guildmates achieve their goals?<br>
<br>
That's what it boils down to, really.  <br>
